# Sky Curtains ‚Äì Business Analytics Case Study

## Overview
This repository contains an end-to-end business analytics case study for **Sky Curtains**, a company specializing in electric curtains.

The project demonstrates both **strategic analysis** and **diagnostic analysis** using the same raw dataset.

